        <mxCell id="descPanel" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacing=14;fillColor=#FFFFFF;strokeColor=#232F3E;fontSize=11;fontColor=#232F3E;spacingTop=15;spacingLeft=15;" value="&lt;h2 style=&quot;margin:0 0 6px 0;color:#232F3E&quot;&gt;ServiceTrack · Descrição dos elementos&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;font-size:10px;color:#666;margin-bottom:10px&quot;&gt;Fonte de verdade: infra/terraform + infra/k8s. Formato: Elemento · Serviço/Ícone · O que é · Origem.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;color:#8C4FFF&quot;&gt;REDE&lt;/b&gt;&lt;ul style=&quot;margin:4px 0 8px 16px;padding:0&quot;&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;VPC&lt;/b&gt; · VPC · servicetrack-dev-vpc, 10.0.0.0/16, DNS on · &lt;i&gt;vpc.tf&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Internet Gateway&lt;/b&gt; · IGW · borda internet da VPC · &lt;i&gt;vpc.tf&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Public Subnets (2)&lt;/b&gt; · Subnet · 10.0.0.0/20 (1a), 10.0.16.0/20 (1b), map_public_ip, tag role/elb · &lt;i&gt;vpc.tf&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Private Subnets (2)&lt;/b&gt; · Subnet · 10.0.48.0/20 (1a), 10.0.64.0/20 (1b), tag role/internal-elb · &lt;i&gt;vpc.tf&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;NAT Gateway (1)&lt;/b&gt; + &lt;b&gt;Elastic IP&lt;/b&gt; · na subnet pública 1a · &lt;i&gt;vpc.tf&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Route Table pública&lt;/b&gt; · 0.0.0.0/0 → IGW (2 subnets) · &lt;i&gt;vpc.tf&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Route Table privada&lt;/b&gt; · 0.0.0.0/0 → NAT (2 subnets) · &lt;i&gt;vpc.tf&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Elastic Load Balancer&lt;/b&gt; · ELB · provisionado pelo Service service-track-app-lb (LoadBalancer, 80→8080) nas subnets públicas · &lt;i&gt;k8s/service-lb.yaml&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;color:#ED7100&quot;&gt;COMPUTE / EKS&lt;/b&gt;&lt;ul style=&quot;margin:4px 0 8px 16px;padding:0&quot;&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;EKS Control Plane&lt;/b&gt; · Amazon EKS · servicetrack-dev, v1.30, subnets públicas + privadas · &lt;i&gt;eks.tf&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Node Group (ASG)&lt;/b&gt; · Auto Scaling · servicetrack-dev-ng, t3.medium, desired 2 / min 1 / max 3, subnets privadas · &lt;i&gt;eks.tf&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Worker Nodes (2)&lt;/b&gt; · EC2 · 1 por AZ · &lt;i&gt;eks.tf&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Pod service-track-app&lt;/b&gt; · K8s Pod · :8080, imagem do ECR, escala via HPA · &lt;i&gt;k8s/deployment.yaml&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Pod service-track-postgres&lt;/b&gt; · K8s Pod · postgres:16-alpine, :5432, emptyDir (efêmero) · &lt;i&gt;k8s/postgres.yaml&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Deployment&lt;/b&gt; · K8s Deploy · service-track-app, replicas geridas pelo HPA · &lt;i&gt;k8s/deployment.yaml&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;HPA&lt;/b&gt; · K8s HPA · 2→10, cpu 70% / mem 80% · &lt;i&gt;k8s/hpa.yaml&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Service (ClusterIP)&lt;/b&gt; · K8s SVC · service-track-app 80→8080 · &lt;i&gt;k8s/service.yaml&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;ConfigMap + Secrets&lt;/b&gt; · K8s CM/Secret · env, JWT keys, RESEND_API_KEY · &lt;i&gt;k8s/configmap.yaml, secret.yaml&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;IAM Role LabRole&lt;/b&gt; · IAM · usada por cluster + node group · &lt;i&gt;eks.tf&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;color:#2E27AD&quot;&gt;DADOS&lt;/b&gt;&lt;ul style=&quot;margin:4px 0 8px 16px;padding:0&quot;&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;RDS PostgreSQL&lt;/b&gt; · Amazon RDS · servicetrack-dev-postgres, pg 16.9, db.t3.micro, gp3 20GB encrypt, single-AZ, não público · &lt;i&gt;rds.tf&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;DB Subnet Group&lt;/b&gt; · RDS · cobre as 2 subnets privadas · &lt;i&gt;rds.tf&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;SG servicetrack-dev-rds-sg&lt;/b&gt; · Security Group · ingress 5432 só do SG do EKS; egress liberado · &lt;i&gt;rds.tf&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;color:#7AA116&quot;&gt;REGISTRO / ESTADO&lt;/b&gt;&lt;ul style=&quot;margin:4px 0 8px 16px;padding:0&quot;&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Amazon ECR&lt;/b&gt; · ECR · service-track-app, MUTABLE, scan-on-push, force_delete · &lt;i&gt;ecr.tf&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Amazon S3&lt;/b&gt; · S3 · Terraform state, servicetrack-tfstate-123124496645, encrypt + lockfile · &lt;i&gt;versions.tf&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;color:#E7157B&quot;&gt;EXTERNO&lt;/b&gt;&lt;ul style=&quot;margin:4px 0 0 16px;padding:0&quot;&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Resend (SMTP)&lt;/b&gt; · e-mail · pods app enviam via smtp.resend.com:587, saída privada → NAT → IGW → internet · &lt;i&gt;k8s/configmap.yaml, secret.yaml&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="540" width="820" x="2260" y="70" as="geometry" />
